  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Alpin Juwel has all the qualities to make it the ideal spot for your next ski holiday. Newly built in 2012 and run by the Schwabl family, this contemporary-style hotel has become a favourite in the Hinterglemm region for its local cuisine, unique wellness area, and central location.</p>
<h3>Central Location</h3>
<p>The hotel is located in the village centre next to the piste with easy access to the U-bahn and Reiterkogel lifts.</p>
<h3>Local Food</h3>
<p>The chefs at Alpin Juwel believe in supporting local community through their food. They work with organic vegetables, local dairy products and home-made breads. In the hotel’s two restaurants you will find seasonal Austrian cuisine made from ingredients from the Saalbach Hinterglemm region. After dinner, the wine bar and cocktail lounge are the perfect place to unwind.</p>
<h3>Wellness Area</h3>
<p>The spa &amp; wellness area features indoor and outdoor pools, saunas, relaxation rooms and gym facilities. The over the edge infinity pool is a favourite of ours, as it gives panoramic views over the mountains. Take your pick of relaxation methods, from massage treatments to daily yoga sessions, or try something new with their specialised Sri Lankan Ayurveda therapies.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 1 hour 45 minutes by coach from Salzburg airport.</p>]]></description>
