  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Kunstkristall Eaves</strong> rooms are located in the hotel's eaves. They are 20m², have a balcony and can sleep two adults.</p>
<p><strong>Double Kristall</strong> rooms have Austrian twin beds and around 23m² of space. They include a balcony, shower, bath,<span> and can sleep up to three adults using a single sofa bed.</span></p>
<p><strong>Junior Suite Kristall</strong> rooms are larger again with 45m² of space including a seating area and balcony. They<span> can sleep up to four adults using a double sofa bed.</span></p>
<p><strong>Apartment Kristall</strong> rooms have a separate lounge area and are available with and without a balcony. </p>
<p><span><strong>Double Rubin</strong> rooms are decorated in a more contemporary style, have 35m² of space and a balcony. They can sleep up to four adults using a double sofa bed.</span></p>
<p><span><strong>Junior Suite Rubin </strong>are decorated in the same style and have 38m² of space including a seating area and balcony. They can sleep up to four adults using a double sofa bed.</span></p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cable / satellite TV</li>
<li>Minibar / fridge</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
